# BottleRocket

This project was created to show the use of Android LiveData in a simple app, for now the app only shows a list of stores, the details of a selected store in a second screen and the option to show store location in Google Maps. The data is fetch from two sources a REST API and an internal database.

## Built With

* [Retrofit2](https://square.github.io/retrofit/) - Type-safe REST client for Android.
* [Realm](https://realm.io/products/realm-database) - Database used for this project.
* [Glide](https://bumptech.github.io/glide/) - Glide is a fast and efficient image loading library for Android focused on smooth scrolling.

